title: My Body Is A Six Flags
description: It's that time again... it's an ALL VOICEMAIL POD! The KAJ gets into all of your important questions, starting with... who is Travis? Then they're asked about what reality shows they'd crush (13:40), the best TV theme song (26:00), their cover band (46:45), the weirdest thing in their notes app (53:30), their Real Housewives tagline (1:08:30), and what fantasy universe they'd live in (1:21:00). Dive in right now.
